N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 112.6 - Plants and propagules

State Regulations
(a) Plants grown from certified seed may be certified the same category as the seed
lot and will be so labeled including lot number. (b) Propagules from certified clones may be
certified the same category as the ortet and will be so labeled. Notes
